# Design System Rules

- Read docs/design/DESIGN_REFERENCE.md before writing any React component
- Open docs/design/prototype-v4.html to see the target visual output
- Use only Tailwind colour tokens from src/App.css @theme — no hardcoded hex values
- Dark mode surface hierarchy:
    bg-background-dark (#1B1D21) — page background
    bg-panel-dark      (#23262B) — panel/card surface
    border-border-dark (#2D3139) — all borders
- Active state: bg-primary/10 text-primary (tinted, not solid fill)
- Primary buttons only: bg-primary text-white
- font-display for UI text, font-mono for all code/monospace content
- All icons use Material Symbols Outlined (icon name as text content in <span>)

## Constants from src/constants/library.ts
Only `categorySubtitles` is exported from this file. Import it when needed.
Category icons and display categories are derived from the registry via
`getDisplayCategories()` — do not hardcode them in components.
